### ðŸ”¹ Project

* [+] `Clean architecture`
* [+] `At least 12 gRPC Endpoints`
* [+] `Usage of Message Queue (preferably NATS)`
* [+] `Usage of Databases and Caches (including migrations and transactions)`
* [+] `Sending Emails (using microsoft or google accounts for SMTP servers)`
* [+] `Testing (Unit and Integrations tests)`
* [-] `Bonus: Grafana`
* [-] `Bonus: Front-End`
